model

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Customer

  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    The "Customer" class represents a single customer. This customer will enter their personal information voluntarily so that the business can gather demographics of their customers. For example, which age groups are buying which products? Where are the majority of their customers located? What are people buying most?
